## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-161">O exemplo a seguir mostra como chamar uma função de script em um documento de um [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] aplicativo usando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-161">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e0958-162">Neste exemplo, a função de script não tem parâmetros.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-162">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-163">A seguir está o [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documento que implementa a função de script que será chamada de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-163">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-164">A seguir mostra o [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementação para chamar a função de script no [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-164">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-172"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> não deve ser chamado antes que o documento que implementa terminou o carregamento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-172"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e0958-173">Você pode detectar quando um documento terminou o carregamento manipulando o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> evento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-173">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-174">Se você não passar suficiente valores de parâmetro para o script que você está invocando, os parâmetros que você não passar valores para terá o valor indefinido.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-174">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e0958-175">Se você passar muitos valores de parâmetro, os valores em excesso são ignorados.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-175">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-176">O exemplo a seguir mostra como chamar funções de script em um documento de um aplicativo usando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-176">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e0958-177">Neste exemplo, as funções de script requerem parâmetros.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-177">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-178">Este é o documento que implementa as funções de script que serão chamadas de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-178">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-179">A seguir mostra o [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementação para chamar o script funciona no [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-179">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-193">Chamando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> tem o mesmo efeito que definir o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> propriedade.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-193">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e0958-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> é usado na marcação por desenvolvedores que desejam especificar declarativamente inicial de documento que <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navega quando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> é inicializado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-195">Use o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> método para navegar até uma URL que pode incluir caracteres de escape.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-195">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e0958-196">Use o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> método para navegar até um <xref:System.Uri> que não inclua caracteres de escape.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-197">O exemplo a seguir mostra como usar <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> para navegar para um documento usando o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> método.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-197">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-215">Use o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> método para navegar até uma URL que pode incluir caracteres de escape.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-215">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e0958-216">Use o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> método para navegar até um <xref:System.Uri> que não inclua caracteres de escape.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-216">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-217">O exemplo a seguir mostra como navegar para um documento e abri-lo em uma nova janela do navegador, especificando o "sobre: em branco" destino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-217">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-226">Se o `stream` parâmetro é `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navega para um documento em branco ("sobre: em branco").</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-226">If the `stream` parameter is `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to a blank document ("about:blank").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-227">Se o parâmetro de fluxo não está em um arquivo [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] formato, ele será exibido como texto sem formatação.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-227">If the stream parameter is not in a valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-228">Depois de navegação, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> será `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-228">After navigation, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> will be `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e0958-229">O exemplo a seguir mostra como navegar em um fluxo que contém um documento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e0958-229">The following example shows how to navigate to a stream that contains a document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateToStreamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Load HTML document as a stream  
  Uri uri = new Uri(@"pack://application:,,,/HTMLDocumentWithScript.html", UriKind.Absolute);  
  Stream source = Application.GetResourceStream(uri).Stream;  
  
  // Navigate to HTML document stream  
  this.webBrowser.NavigateToStream(source);  
}  
```

  
  
